<p>AOK is Application Lifecycle Service's authentication management service (replacing Cloud Foundry's UAA Server). It issues tokens via OAuth2 for client applications such as the <b>helion</b> client and the Horizon Console. AOK can connect to other back-end SSO services such as LDAP by using different <xref type="section" href="#topic8432/aok-strategies">
<i>Strategies</i>
